# 10c. Test Drive Interrupt
sysbus.spi1.mySensor Transmit 0x62
sysbus.spi1.mySensor Transmit 0x40
sysbus.spi1.mySensor FinishTransmission

# 10d. Test Drive DRDY
sysbus.spi1.mySensor Transmit 0x62
sysbus.spi1.mySensor Transmit 0x01
sysbus.spi1.mySensor FinishTransmission

# 10e. Test Reserved Bits
